{"id":79269,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/06/【从同盟到交恶：中朝关系凸视镜】：⑬-中朝关系/","date":"2010-06-18T21:58:41Z","modified":"2010-06-18T21:58:41Z","title":"【从同盟到交恶：中朝关系凸视镜】：⑬ 中朝关系再思考","content":"<p><h1><span>原文: </span><span><b><a href=\"http://china.joins.com/portal/article.do?method=detail&#038;total_id=4222889\" title=\"[혈맹서 애증까지:고수석의 북・중 돋보기] ⑬ 중국과 북한을 다시 생각하며\">[혈맹서 애증까지:고수석의 북・중 돋보기] ⑬ 중국과 북한을 다시 생각하며</a></b></span></h1>\n<h1><span>译文: </span><span><span>【从同盟到交恶：中朝关系凸视镜】：</span>⑬ <span>中朝关系再思考</span></span></h1>\n<div><span><span>作者：<a href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\" name=\"OLE_LINK12\"></a><a href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\" name=\"OLE_LINK11\"></a><span><span>고수석</span></span><br />发表时间：<span><span>2010-06-07 <span>  上午</span></span></span><span><span> 09:39:01</span></span><br />译者：jjtily</span></span></div>\n<p><span><br /></span><br /><span>“猫</span><span>头鹰</span><span>的一</span><span>个</span><span>特点是在</span><span>黄</span><span>昏起</span><span>飞</span><span>”</span><span>，</span><span> </span><span>这</span><span>是德</span><span>国</span><span>哲</span><span>学</span><span>家黑格尔在《法哲</span><span>学</span><span>》中的名言。</span><span>对</span><span>事</span><span>务真</span><span>理的</span><span>认识总</span><span>是要在事情</span><span>发</span><span>生之后才更准确。在上一篇文章中，</span><span>笔</span><span>者</span><span>断</span><span>言金正日不</span><span>会访华</span><span>，</span><span>现</span><span>在事</span><span>实</span><span>已</span><span>经证</span><span>明是</span><span>错误</span><span>的（</span><span>这</span><span>里回</span><span>顾</span><span>上一篇</span><span>一个细节</span><span>，上一篇作者猜</span><span>测</span><span>金正日不</span><span>会访华</span><span>是因</span><span>为</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>已</span><span>经没</span><span>有什</span><span>么</span><span>大</span><span>礼</span><span>再援助朝</span><span>鲜</span><span>了。据</span><span>报</span><span>道，</span><span>温</span><span>家</span><span>宝</span><span>拒</span><span>绝</span><span>了</span><span>对</span><span>朝援助要求，</span><span>结</span><span>果金正日提前</span><span>结</span><span>束</span><span>访华</span><span>回</span><span>国</span><span>。</span><span>译</span><span>者注）。</span></p>\n<p><span>3</span><span>月26日，天安</span><span>号</span><span>沉</span><span>没</span><span>，</span><span>5</span><span>月3日，金正日</span><span>访华</span><span>，整</span><span>个过</span><span>程成</span><span>为</span><span>分析中朝</span><span>关</span><span>系的又一</span><span>个</span><span>机</span><span>会</span><span>。中</span><span>国</span><span>第四代</span><span>领导</span><span>人</span><span>们</span><span>秉承“和平</span><span>发</span><span>展”理念，站在</span><span>国现实</span><span>主</span><span>义</span><span>立</span><span>场</span><span>，</span><span>为</span><span>了</span><span>国</span><span>家利益最大化，又希望在</span><span>国际</span><span>上突出大</span><span>国</span><span>地位……中</span><span>国</span><span>表</span><span>现</span><span>出了自信。</span><span>一位</span><span>中</span><span>国学</span><span>者就此</span><span>说</span><span>中朝</span><span>关</span><span>系已</span><span>经从过</span><span>去的同盟中走出</span><span>来</span><span>，</span><span>现</span><span>在</span><span>是</span><span>正常的</span><span>国</span><span>家</span><span>关系</span><span>，</span><span>他用</span><span>来证</span><span>明的事例就是</span><span>两</span><span>次朝核危机中</span><span>国</span><span>表</span><span>现</span><span>出的</span><span>对</span><span>朝立</span><span>场</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span>显</span><span>然</span><span>这种结论属</span><span>于幻想，中</span><span>国与</span><span>北朝</span><span>鲜给</span><span>人的印象仍然是重要的盟友。中</span><span>国</span><span>在</span><span>国际</span><span>敏感</span><span>时</span><span>期邀</span><span>请</span><span>金正日，</span><span>显然是要</span><span>直接听到金正日</span><span>关</span><span>于天安</span><span>号事件</span><span>的申</span><span>辩</span><span>。</span><span>不管</span><span>怎么说</span><span>，金正日</span><span>访</span><span>中</span><span>时</span><span>，朝</span><span>鲜</span><span>是天安</span><span>号</span><span>元凶已</span><span>经</span><span>基本成</span><span>为</span><span>定</span><span>论</span><span>。李明博</span><span>访问</span><span>上海</span><span>也</span><span>刚刚过</span><span>去</span><span>4</span><span>天，在</span><span>与</span><span>胡</span><span>锦涛</span><span>的</span><span>会</span><span>面中</span><span>，这位韩国总统</span><span>表</span><span>达</span><span>了</span><span>对</span><span>中</span><span>国态</span><span>度的不</span><span>满</span><span>，</span><span>韩国</span><span>民</span><span>众显</span><span>然更</span><span>气</span><span>氛，“中</span><span>国怎</span><span>能如此？”</span></p>\n<p><span>考</span><span>虑</span><span>到中</span><span>国</span><span>的立</span><span>场</span><span>和金正日的健康，</span><span>笔者</span><span>曾判</span><span>断</span><span>金正日不</span><span>会访华</span><span>。</span><span>不</span><span>过</span><span>看</span><span>来</span><span>金正日的健康比想象中的要好的多</span><span>。</span><span>笔</span><span>者</span><span>虽</span><span>然一直</span><span>研</span><span>究中朝</span><span>关</span><span>系，</span><span>还</span><span>是</span><span>存在浪漫的幻想。</span></p>\n<p><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>主</span><span>义国</span><span>家之</span><span>间</span><span>，党</span><span>对</span><span>党的交往</span><span>显</span><span>得比</span><span>国</span><span>家</span><span>与国</span><span>家的交往更密切。</span><span>为</span><span>什</span><span>么</span><span>？社</span><span>会</span><span>主</span><span>义</span><span>主</span><span>张</span><span>世界革命，党</span><span>对</span><span>党之</span><span>间</span><span>目</span><span>标</span><span>是一致的，不像</span><span>国</span><span>家</span><span>与国</span><span>家之</span><span>间</span><span>可能</span><span>会产</span><span>生</span><span>国</span><span>家利益的冲突。天安</span><span>号</span><span>、核</span><span>试验显</span><span>然</span><span>属</span><span>于</span><span>国</span><span>家</span><span>间</span><span>的冲突</span><span>与</span><span>摩擦，不</span><span>会</span><span>影</span><span>响</span><span>党</span><span>对</span><span>党的</span><span>关系</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span>除了邀</span><span>请</span><span>金正日</span><span>访华，让韩国国</span><span>民不理解的，</span><span>还</span><span>有</span><span>中国</span><span>对</span><span>金正日的破格接待。中</span><span>国对</span><span>金正日的招待</span><span>真</span><span>可</span><span>谓</span><span>超</span><span>规</span><span>格</span><span>，</span><span>政治局九位常委都</span><span>见</span><span>了金正日，李克强被重点介</span><span>绍</span><span>。其</span><span>实这</span><span>些是中朝</span><span>双</span><span>方交往的</span><span>惯</span><span>例，</span><span>从</span><span>1958</span><span>年金日成第一次</span><span>访华</span><span>就</span><span>开</span><span>始了。到</span><span>1958</span><span>年10月26日，中</span><span>国</span><span>人民志愿</span><span>军</span><span>已</span><span>经</span><span>完全</span><span>从</span><span>朝</span><span>鲜</span><span>撤出，</span><span>两国关</span><span>系正常化，中</span><span>国</span><span>邀</span><span>请</span><span>金日成正式</span><span>访华</span><span>。</span><span>1958</span><span>年11月21~28日，金日成第一次</span><span>访华</span><span>，</span><span>为</span><span>了迎接金日成，中</span><span>国专门</span><span>派政府高官去</span><span>两国边</span><span>境丹</span><span>东</span><span>迎接，金日成的</span><span>专</span><span>列到</span><span>达</span><span>北京</span><span>时</span><span>，包括周恩</span><span>来总</span><span>理在</span><span>内</span><span>的党和</span><span>国</span><span>家高</span><span>级</span><span>干部</span><span>们</span><span>都去了火</span><span>车</span><span>站迎接</span><span>。</span><span>当</span><span>然，</span><span>这种</span><span>破格是相互的，每次中</span><span>国</span><span>最高</span><span>领导</span><span>人</span><span>访</span><span>朝</span><span>时</span><span>，金日成也</span><span>会</span><span>到平壤机</span><span>场</span><span>迎接。</span></p>\n<p><span>2012</span><span>年之后，中朝党</span><span>对</span><span>党的</span><span>关</span><span>系</span><span>还会继续维</span><span>持</span><span>传统</span><span>。天安</span><span>号</span><span>沉没</span><span>，北朝</span><span>鲜</span><span>再次陷入四面楚歌，中</span><span>国</span><span>的立</span><span>场</span><span>却稍微倒退，中</span><span>国</span><span>的表</span><span>现与国际</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>的期望相差很大。</span><span>联</span><span>合</span><span>国对</span><span>朝</span><span>鲜将会</span><span>采取什</span><span>么样</span><span>的制裁</span><span>现</span><span>在</span><span>还</span><span>不知道，中</span><span>国应该会</span><span>共同</span><span>参与</span><span>，即中</span><span>国与国际</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>的步</span><span>调</span><span>保持一致。但是，</span><span>国际</span><span>社</span><span>会</span><span>期望的中</span><span>国单独对</span><span>朝施</span><span>压</span><span>，中</span><span>国却</span><span>表</span><span>现</span><span>消</span><span>极</span><span>，原因在于中</span><span>国对</span><span>北朝</span><span>鲜独</span><span>占的</span><span>国</span><span>家利益。</span></p>\n<p><span>这次</span><span>金正日</span><span>访</span><span>中</span><span>，是</span><span>北朝</span><span>鲜</span><span>党、政、</span><span>军实</span><span>力派</span><span>的一次总动员</span><span>。</span><span>随行人员</span><span>包括咸</span><span>镜</span><span>南道和平安北道的</span><span>书记</span><span>是很</span><span>让</span><span>人以外的。</span><span>两个</span><span>地方都是中</span><span>国</span><span>很</span><span>关</span><span>心的</span><span>地区</span><span>，</span><span>咸</span><span>镜</span><span>南道是世界上</span><span>铅锌</span><span>主要</span><span>产区</span><span>，平安北道</span><span>与</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>接壤，是正</span><span>进</span><span>行特</span><span>区开发</span><span>的地</span><span>区</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>是大</span><span>国</span><span>，</span><span>与韩国</span><span>相比，中</span><span>国</span><span>要考</span><span>虑</span><span>的事情更多。</span><span>虽</span><span>然中</span><span>国</span><span>立</span><span>场</span><span>如此，</span><span>韩国</span><span>也不能表</span><span>现</span><span>出不快。因</span><span>为</span><span>中</span><span>国</span><span>无法置自己的</span><span>国</span><span>家利益不</span><span>顾</span><span>。</span><span>对韩国来说</span><span>，中朝交往是中</span><span>国与</span><span>朝</span><span>鲜两国</span><span>的</span><span>内</span><span>政。知己知彼，百</span><span>战</span><span>不殆。我</span><span>们对</span><span>于中</span><span>国</span><span>和北朝</span><span>鲜还</span><span>需要</span><span>认真学习</span><span>。</span></p>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<p><b>相关阅读：</b></p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0B3C6I8b9sUt9ZDBlMWJmNDktM2Q0Zi00MWEyLTkyNDctNTYwY2M3M2UyN2U4&#038;sort=name&#038;layout=list&#038;num=50\" title=\"译者的“jjtily”专题\">译者的“jjtily”专题</a><br /></b></p>\n<p><span>说明</span>：感谢韩文译者jjtily的持续努力，我们将把《<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0B3C6I8b9sUt9ZDBlMWJmNDktM2Q0Zi00MWEyLTkyNDctNTYwY2M3M2UyN2U4&#038;sort=name&#038;layout=list&#038;num=50\" title=\"从同盟到交恶\">从同盟到交恶</a>》的完整系列，加上他和其他译者翻译的关于北韩的所有资料进行整合，争取本月发出“中朝关系”的一个完整的合集。敬请期待。</p>\n<p><span>来源说明：本文1.0版本来源译者的志愿翻译者团队。</span><br /><span>收录说明：本文已经收录到“译者文集”中，同时进入“中央日报”、“译者jjtily”、“译者频道—看世界”索引。</span></p>\n<div>\n<div><span><i>©译者遵守<a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/2.5/cn/\" title=\"CC协议2.5\">CC协议2.5</a>您可以自由复制、发行、展览、表演、放映、广播或通过信息网络传播，创作演绎本作品。惟须遵守下列条件：署名，非商业性使用，相同方式共享。</i></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-707273691137144025?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p>来源 <a href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">译者</a>:<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/2010/06/blog-post_09.html\" title=\"【从同盟到交恶：中朝关系凸视镜】：⑬ 中朝关系再思考\">【从同盟到交恶：中朝关系凸视镜】：⑬ 中朝关系再思考</a></p>\n","author":139,"categories":[9203],"tags":[5908,9980]}